<p><b>Instant messaging</b> (<b>IM</b>) is a form of <a href="/wiki/Real-time_computing" title="Real-time computing">real-time</a> communication between two or more <a href="/wiki/People" title="People">people</a> based on typed text. The <a href="/wiki/Written_language" title="Written language">text</a> is conveyed via devices connected over a network such as the <a href="/wiki/Internet" title="Internet">Internet</a>.</p>
